%section#wv-sundays
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-12
        %h1 sundays - what to expect
        %p We start about 10:30am, but most people come along about 15 to 20 minutes early for a cup of proper coffee. The kids groups open for check in about 10:20am.
    .row
      .col-md-4
        %h3 we start with worship
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/worship.jpg'}
        %p We always have a live band playing music for about 30 minutes at the beginning of the service. They play a mixture of loud and quiet contemporary songs and hymns. The words are shown on a screen: feel free to join in, or sit and watch if you prefer.
      .col-md-4
        %h3 learn together
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/insight.jpg'}
        %p
          After the music, there's a talk given by someone in the church or a visiting speaker based on the bible. It's not just theory: there's always ways to apply what's being shared to our day to day lives.
          %br
          %a{:href => '#wv-talks'} Listen to recordings of past talks &raquo;
      .col-md-4
        %h3 and make a response
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/response.jpg'}
        %p We believe in the supernatural. Often during the morning God speaks to people about medical conditions that others in the room have. We always have time to pray for people for emotional and physical at this point in the morning.
    .row
      .col-sm-6
        %h3 kids church and youth
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/kids-church.jpg'}
        %p Church isn't only for adults. Rather than just schooling kids on Sundays, we run a variety of interactive groups for under 11s learning about Jesus with games and fun at the centre! We also have a great bunch of 11-18 year olds who meet each sunday morning in the upstairs youth room.
      .col-sm-6
        %h3 coffee and cake
        %img{:src => '/images/photos/areas/sunday/coffee.jpg'}
        %p We finish up around noon, when parents collect their younger kids from their groups. We serve lovely cakes and nice coffee or teas and have a large cafÃ© area for everyone to hang out. People often stick around for almost an hour to chat!
